#: lib/tuist_web/live/module_cache_live.html.heex:115
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Cache hit rate represents the percentage of cacheable targets that were resolved from cache (local or remote) rather than being rebuilt."
msgstr "La tasa de aciertos de caché representa el porcentaje de objetivos cacheables que se resolvieron desde la caché (local o remota) en lugar de ser recompilados."

#: lib/tuist_web/live/xcode_cache_live.html.heex:113
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Cache hit rate represents the percentage of cacheable tasks that were resolved from cache (local or remote) rather than being rebuilt."
msgstr "La tasa de aciertos de caché representa el porcentaje de tareas cacheables que se resolvieron desde la caché (local o remota) en lugar de ser recompiladas."

#: lib/tuist_web/live/module_cache_live.ex:277
